, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdur Rahman ibn Ghanm reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever says ten times before departing the sunset and dawn prayers or moving his feet, \u2018There is no God but Allah alone, without any partners, to Him belong the dominion and all praise, all goodness is\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38426,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/11\/01\/powerful-dua-nahar-wa-layl\/","url_meta":{"origin":34758,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Powerful supplication to Allah, morning and evening","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 1, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Ayyub reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever says ten times when he awakens in the morning, \u2018There is no God but Allah, alone without any partners to Him. He owns the dominion and for Him is all praise. He gives life and causes death,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38456,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/11\/09\/dua-dhikr-after-fajr\/","url_meta":{"origin":34758,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Fajr: Rewards for supplication after dawn prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 9, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Umamah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever says one hundred times after dawn prayer before moving his feet, \u2018There is no God but Allah, without any partners. He owns the dominion and to Him is all praise, He gives life and He\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11763,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/24\/hamdulillah-ala-kul-hal\/","url_meta":{"origin":34758,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Tahmid: The Prophet praises Allah in every situation","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 24, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: If the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, saw something he liked, he would say, \u201cAll praise is due to Allah, by whose favor good deeds are accomplished.\u201d If the Prophet\u00a0saw something he disliked, he would say, \u201cAll praise is due to Allah in every\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25144,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/08\/09\/dua-nawm-waking-up\/","url_meta":{"origin":34758,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Dua: The Prophet\u2019s supplication for sleep, waking up","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 9, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Hudhayfah reported: When the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, laid down at night, he would place his hand under his cheek and then say, \u201cO Allah, in Your name I die and I live.\u201d When the Prophet would awaken, he would say, \u201cAll praise is due to Allah,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\